  "body": "#### System information\r\n- Erigon version: 2022.09.01-alpha\r\n- OS & Version: Linux\r\n\r\n#### Problem\r\n\r\nFor [this tx](https://goerli.etherscan.io/tx/0x08d3efbbd3d388b132c42b0030cf10ee95ebdd1632439e21dc1acb97c16462f4) the tx fee is 115931998956612 wei but the trace shows a balance change for the miner of 149004998658955 wei. \r\n```\r\n        \"0x25c4a76e7d118705e7ea2e9b7d8c59930d8acd3b\": {\r\n          \"balance\": {\r\n            \"*\": {\r\n              \"from\": \"0x7d4b22dd1c4eccdee\",\r\n              \"to\": \"0x7d4b2b556b2f09979\"\r\n            }\r\n          },\r\n          \"code\": \"=\",\r\n          \"nonce\": \"=\",\r\n          \"storage\": {}\r\n        },\r\n        \"0x6c287e19065661ca590a11cf0b419d1434991b67\": {\r\n          \"balance\": {\r\n            \"*\": {\r\n              \"from\": \"0x21eb2ee29ea0734d\",\r\n              \"to\": \"0x21eaa75db085eb40\"\r\n            }\r\n          },\r\n          \"code\": \"=\",\r\n          \"nonce\": {\r\n            \"*\": {\r\n              \"from\": \"0x1558\",\r\n              \"to\": \"0x1559\"\r\n            }\r\n          },\r\n          \"storage\": {}\r\n        }\r\n      },\r\n      \"trace\": [],\r\n      \"vmTrace\": null,\r\n      \"transactionHash\": \"0x08d3efbbd3d388b132c42b0030cf10ee95ebdd1632439e21dc1acb97c16462f4\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n[Etherscan shows this as well](https://goerli.etherscan.io/tx/0x08d3efbbd3d388b132c42b0030cf10ee95ebdd1632439e21dc1acb97c16462f4#statechange)\r\n\r\nThe diff between the actual reward received by miner and state diff is 33072999702343 wei. The stateDiff reports the amount the miner would have received if the full gasLimit was used 149,005 when in fact only 115,932 gas was used\r\n\r\nCan someone help me understand why the trace does not show the correct balance change for the miner?\r\n\r\nYou can verify that the sum of balances differences for the miner (0x25c4a76e7d118705e7ea2e9b7d8c59930d8acd3b) in the trace (all the tx fees they received) != the balance change before and after the block, with a difference of the 33072999702343 wei",
